%% FMS Guardrails Orchestrator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS / caikit-nlp<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as vLLM / OpenAI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/4318/TCP

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (Unary)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Tokenized chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (input detection)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (input)
    Orch->>TGIS: Generate / GenerateStream<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (output detection)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (output)
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response (text + detections)

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: Input detection<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS
    OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Detector: Output detection<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    Chunker-->>Orch: Tokenized chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON Response (detections)

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 4: Health Check
    Client->>Health: GET /health (8034/TCP plaintext)
    Health->>Detector: Health probe (8081/TCP)
    Detector-->>Health: Health status
    Health-->>Client: Health status JSON

    Note over Orch,OTLP: Continuous: Observability
    Orch->>OTLP: Traces + Metrics<br/>gRPC/4317 or HTTP/4318
